<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Dokumentasi API untuk layanan URL Shortener.">
    <title>Dokumentasi API - URL Shortener</title>
    
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body { background-color: #121212; color: #ffffff; }
        .navbar { background-color: #1e1e1e; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; }
        .card { background-color: #1e1e1e; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; }
        pre { background-color: #222; color: #00ff99; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> URL Shortener</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light"><i class="fa-solid fa-home"></i> Beranda</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="text-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-book"></i> Dokumentasi API</h1>
        <p class="text-muted text-center">Panduan lengkap penggunaan API URL Shortener</p>

        <div class="card">
            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-compress"></i> 1. Perpendek URL</h2>
            <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>POST /api/shorten</code></p>
            <p><strong>Request:</strong></p>
            <pre>
{
    "longUrl": "https://example.com"
}
            </pre>
            <p><strong>Response:</strong></p>
            <pre>
{
    "shortUrl": "http://localhost:3000/abc123"
}
            </pre>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt-4">
            <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i> 2. Redirect URL</h2>
            <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>GET /:shortCode</code></p>
            <p>Gunakan URL pendek yang dihasilkan untuk mengakses URL asli.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>